{"tid":542484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【周庭被DQ】有官員表示要「註銷」一代年輕人","createTime":"2018-01-27T13:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T05:24:42.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d3018d6dd5b1ad4597c61aa087b15261d0e63d0d","tid":542484,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:38:00.000Z","msg":"立法會議員邵家臻今日（27日）於今日周庭回應被DQ記者會上，提到曾聽到有官員稱要「清洗」這一代年輕人。他其後接受《香港01》查詢時，披露消息來自一位學者朋友，約一年前出席與青年政策相關、討論佔領運動後相關事宜的會議上聽到。朋友於會後氣憤地引述有官員在席上說：「（港府）會Write Off（註銷）呢一代人」。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員葉建源指未有聽聞，認為說法可怕。他指若言論是於前行政長官梁振英時期發表，他認為不無可能，因為根據梁振英的行事作風較對立，其智囊有可能會說出此等言論。"},{"pid":"81a823c8268c8dafc6747d93b6498bb02f1a5f22","tid":542484,"uid":25771,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"曾經聽到。學者朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278eca72dc93c24253ed6fc9b0393969c4c5576e","tid":542484,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:48:17.000Z","msg":"就快小支支都被註銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bd1d1e54cd98eda79c0ec1f8c696144d0b0350","tid":542484,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8147aaad5c95c6e8cd4670c53ce300ae5eefb5","tid":542484,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T13:49:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">根本共狗只放心自己養開班戲子大中狗入議會！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼續大龍鳳含撚保送新舊紅鵪鶉3代盡取港九新3席！！！</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"bc1054cb79c322a91d6adf104a5f789f2d4729f0","tid":542484,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":